text:
Yo Aaishi,
Tere baare mein toh kya hi kahe. 333 mein room ko ganda karke avinash ko pareshaan karna aur mera sara khaane ka saman dheere dheere kha lena. Tere wajah se hi usse lock mein rakhna padta tha mujhe. Galaxy mein tera woh hard work aur wo Cresendo mein teri leadership(Jiski trophy aaj bhi room pe sajake rakhta hai) ke kya hi kehne. Tere bolneke style ka deewana toh pehle se hi tha mein, chahe wo bholleyball ka smas ho ya vaivav. Fifa, poker ya badminton tere saath kuch bhi khelene maaze aate the although tu sab mein haar toh jata tha. But everything aside, tere jesa hardworking and dedicated insaan nahi dekha meine. SAE, Gym, Acads, pingala ke emails ye sab tu itni acche se ek saath handle karta tha, shayad hi aur koi kar pata. I know tu kissi badi company malik banega, and mein tab bhi tere liye apni patented taali bajaunga! And life ka analysis thoda kam kar aur Jald trip plan kar, milenge waha - incomplete photoshoot complete karna hai!ğŸ˜
P.S. Ye kabhi mat bhoolna ki cheekink aane ke baad sorry bolna meine hi sikhaya hai tujhe!ğŸ¤£
author: Kishan Sunil Nawal

text:
Priye anuj(Haalnki umra mein tum mujhe bade ho but still...),
Tumhare jesa helpful insaan nahi dikha. Kabhi madad karne se piche nahi hat ta tha (Shifting ke waqt Aniket aur mere alas ko badhaawa dene ki liye dhanyawadğŸ˜ ). Tum chahe kitni koshish karlo, mere ya aaishi ke rehte room kabhi saaf nahi rakh paoge. Yuhi haste khelte raho, milenge jald!ğŸ˜
Tumhari Seekh mein kabhi nahi bhulungağŸ˜‰
author: Kishan Sunil Nawal

text:
Yo Paaji,
Tumhare jese ethu-wale bande kam hi dekhne milenge. Kissiko bhi convince karne mein mahir. ELS coordi pretend karna(although pretend karna hai toh jis position ki respect hai usse pretend toh karta), phir tooti phooti angrezi mein khudko beizzat karwana and uske baad sympathy leke mere snacks loot lene ka plan hamesha kaam karta tha. Yuhi chhapte raho and aao kabhi haveli pe, tumhe bhi poker khilaynege!
author: Kishan Sunil Nawal
